{
  "stem": "1901.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the Germans never interfered till that day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it happened one week.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I wasn't there, fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Amsterdam is surrounded by canals and water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they lifted all the bridges.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they picked from the street 2,000 boys-- to-- to select 200.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How to find out?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You always drop your pants.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All were circumcised, and I-- And the 200 boys, they were sent to a camp in Holland one day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the next day, the Monday, the whole city was on strike.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And it's a well-known strike, the February strike.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was living in the other part of the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We knew what happened after.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From those boys, one came back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were sent to Mauthausen, and they all were killed, one after the other one.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, we heard it straightaway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, it was immediately it went around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans started.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then we started getting frightened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That is the time, '41.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Then it really start getting bad.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, fright, getting away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But where could we go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was very-- look, we didn't have the right contact.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's very hard to get away.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And all the contacts were not so good because, say, 100 escape, and 90 were picked up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a lot of-- yeah, some of them came to Belgium, Switzerland, and unoccupied France, but very few.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know many of them who really escaped.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have to, you see, in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then I had the diamond spare, and that kept me-- kept me sitting there in Holland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was maybe my-- my-- well, my spare.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was spared.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was free for a while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was not a political, I was not--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To go underground, no, it was too dangerous for us.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
